Experts rally countries to build research capacities The celebrated personality is expected to fly the inaugural flight scheduled for October 28, 2018, for his globally renowned Quest Means Business show. The new flight path will cut down travel time from 22 to 15 hours. The carrier is hoping the highly anticipated direct flights to the US will boost tourism.